WorkItem.ClosedComment: You have 2 Dodge Trinkets and Windwalk, those are being averaged onto your Dodge Rating value. The same goes for the other stats, it's abilities and such averaging onto it.
WorkItem.Description:
Defensive stats in Rawr vary from in game stats, in some cases very dramatically.
 
Rawr(4.1.04) Unbuffed:
Strength: 3308
Armor: 36029
Dodge: 1922.58
Parry: 2200.75
Mastery: 1909
 
In game unbuffed:
Strength:3268
Armor: 36356
Dodge: 1089
Parry:2244
Mastery: 1925
 
Understandable of a certain tolerance for error, but something like dodge being that far off can really throw off calculations, especially the parry:dodge ratio for hold the line.
